# Dropdown — Visual Specification

## Architecture

All visual styling lives in `packages/css/src/dropdown.css` using `@apply` for structural utilities and raw CSS for transitions, animations, and theme overrides.

---

## Class Inventory

### Base
| Class | Purpose |
|---|---|
| `.acko-dropdown` | Wrapper — `flex flex-col gap-1 relative` |
| `.acko-dropdown-label` | Label — typography tokens, `color: var(--color-text-default)` |
| `.acko-dropdown-required` | Required asterisk — `color: var(--color-error)` |
| `.acko-dropdown-trigger` | Trigger button — `flex items-center justify-between w-full rounded-full` |
| `.acko-dropdown-value` | Selected value — `flex-1 min-w-0 overflow-hidden text-overflow:ellipsis` |
| `.acko-dropdown-placeholder` | Placeholder text — `color: var(--color-text-muted)` |
| `.acko-dropdown-chevron` | Chevron icon — `shrink-0 flex items-center ml-2` |
| `.acko-dropdown-menu` | Dropdown menu — `absolute list-none`, shadow, rounded, animated |
| `.acko-dropdown-option` | Single option — `flex items-center gap-2 cursor-pointer` |
| `.acko-dropdown-search` | Search input inside menu — `w-full rounded-full` |

### Sizes
| Class | Height | Padding | Font Size |
|---|---|---|---|
| `.acko-dropdown-trigger-sm` | `h-10` (40px) | `px-4` | `var(--font-body-sm-size)` |
| `.acko-dropdown-trigger-md` | `h-12` (48px) | `px-5` | `var(--font-body-md-size)` |
| `.acko-dropdown-trigger-lg` | `h-14` (56px) | `px-6` | `var(--font-body-lg-size)` |

### Variants
| Variant | Behavior |
|---|---|
| `single` | Select one option, menu closes on select |
| `multi` | Select multiple, shows tags with remove button |
| `searchable` | Adds search input at top of menu |
| `grouped` | Options grouped under headers |

### States
| Class | Effect |
|---|---|
| `.acko-dropdown-trigger-open` | Active/open — `border-color: var(--color-primary); box-shadow: 0 0 0 1px var(--color-primary)` |
| `.acko-dropdown-trigger-error` | Error — `border-color: var(--color-error)`, shake animation |
| `.acko-dropdown-trigger-filled` | Has value — `border-color: var(--color-border-strong)` |
| `.acko-dropdown-trigger:disabled` | Disabled — `cursor-not-allowed`, muted colors |
| `.acko-dropdown-label-open` | Label when open — `color: var(--color-primary)` |
| `.acko-dropdown-label-error` | Label on error — `color: var(--color-error-text)` |
| `.acko-dropdown-option-focused` | Keyboard-focused — `background-color: var(--color-primary-subtle)` |
| `.acko-dropdown-option-selected` | Selected — `var(--color-primary-subtle)` bg, `font-weight: 500` |
| `.acko-dropdown-option-disabled` | Disabled option — `color: var(--color-text-muted); cursor-not-allowed` |

### Multi-select Tags
| Class | Purpose |
|---|---|
| `.acko-dropdown-tags` | Container — `flex flex-wrap gap: --scale-4` |
| `.acko-dropdown-tag` | Individual tag — `inline-flex rounded-full`, primary-subtle bg |
| `.acko-dropdown-tag-remove` | Remove button — `inline-flex bg-transparent`, hover opacity |

### Helper/Error Text
| Class | Color |
|---|---|
| `.acko-dropdown-helper-text` | `var(--color-text-muted)` |
| `.acko-dropdown-error-text` | `var(--color-error-text)` |

---

## Animations

| Keyframe | Purpose |
|---|---|
| `acko-dropdown-menu-enter` | Menu fade-in + translateY(-8px → 0) over 150ms |
| `acko-dropdown-shake` | Error shake — 300ms horizontal oscillation |

---

## Tokens Used

| Token | Usage |
|---|---|
| `--color-input-border` | Default trigger border |
| `--color-surface` | Trigger and menu background |
| `--color-surface-raised` | Dark theme trigger bg |
| `--color-primary` | Open state border, chevron, focus ring |
| `--color-primary-subtle` | Option hover/selected/focused bg |
| `--color-primary-active` | Multi-select tag text |
| `--color-border-strong` | Hover and filled trigger border |
| `--color-text-strong` | Value and option text |
| `--color-text-muted` | Placeholder, helper text, chevron, disabled option |
| `--color-text-disabled` | Disabled trigger text |
| `--color-error` | Required asterisk |
| `--color-error-text` | Error label and text |
| `--shadow-dropdown` | Menu shadow |
| `--z-dropdown` | Menu z-index |
| `--radius-full` | Trigger and tag border-radius |
| `--radius-3xl` | Menu border-radius |
| `--radius-lg` | Option border-radius |
| `--ease-out-cubic` | Chevron rotation, menu animation |

---

## Dark Theme Overrides

- Trigger: `background-color: var(--color-surface-raised)`, `border-color: var(--color-input-border)`
- Error trigger: `border-color: var(--color-error-text)`
- Disabled trigger: `background-color: var(--color-disabled-bg)`
- Menu: `var(--color-surface-raised)` background
- Search: `var(--color-surface)` background

## Elevated Theme Overrides

- Trigger: glass background with gradient border using `padding-box/border-box`, backdrop blur
- Open/focus: `var(--elevated-focus-ring)` shadow
- Hover: `var(--elevated-glow-hover)` shadow
- Menu: glass background + gradient border, 18px blur
